#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.transform.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.transform"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:1 of
msgid "Call ``func`` on self producing a DataFrame with transformed values."
msgstr "在自身上调用 ``func``，生成一个包含转换后值的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:3 of
msgid "Produced DataFrame will have same axis length as self."
msgstr "生成的 DataFrame 将具有与自身相同的轴长度。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:5 of
msgid ""
"Function to use for transforming the data. If a function, must either "
"work when passed a DataFrame or when passed to DataFrame.apply.  Accepted"
" combinations are:  - function - string function name - list of functions"
" and/or function names, e.g. ``[np.exp. 'sqrt']`` - dict of axis labels "
"-> functions, function names or list of such."
msgstr ""
"用于转换数据的函数。如果是一个函数，则必须能够在传入 DataFrame 时工作，"
"或者可以被传递给 DataFrame.apply。可接受的组合包括： - 函数 - 字符串形式"
"的函数名 - 函数和/或函数名的列表，例如 ``[np.exp. 'sqrt']`` - 轴标签到"
"函数、函数名或其列表的字典。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:5 of
msgid ""
"Function to use for transforming the data. If a function, must either "
"work when passed a DataFrame or when passed to DataFrame.apply."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:8 of
msgid "Accepted combinations are:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:10 of
msgid "function"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:11 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "string function name"
msgstr "在 DataFrame 上调用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:12 of
msgid "list of functions and/or function names, e.g. ``[np.exp. 'sqrt']``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:13 of
msgid "dict of axis labels -> functions, function names or list of such."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:15 of
msgid ""
"If 0 or 'index': apply function to each column. If 1 or 'columns': apply "
"function to each row."
msgstr ""
"如果为 0 或 'index'：将函数应用于每一列。如果为 1 或 'columns'：将函数"
"应用于每一行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:18 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 的数据类型。详见“说明”部分。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:20 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:22 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的位置参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:23 of
msgid "Keyword arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:25 of
msgid "A DataFrame that must have the same length as self."
msgstr "一个必须与自身具有相同长度的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:28 of
msgid ""
":raises ValueError : If the returned DataFrame has a different length "
"than self.:"
msgstr ":raises ValueError : 如果返回的 DataFrame 与自身的长度不同。:"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.agg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:33 of
msgid "Only perform aggregating type operations."
msgstr "仅执行聚合类型的操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:36 of
msgid "Invoke function on a DataFrame."
msgstr "在 DataFrame 上调用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.df_transform:40 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock DataFrame and the apply call may fail. "
"When this happens, you need to specify a list or a pandas Series as "
"``dtypes`` of output DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"在确定输出数据类型和返回值形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用于一个"
"模拟 DataFrame，此时 apply 调用可能失败。发生这种情况时，你需要指定一个"
"列表或 pandas Series 作为输出 DataFrame 的 ``dtypes``。"

